            <title>[FLINK-14454] Usages of SavepointSerializers.setFailWhenLegacyStateDetected are never reverted</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-14454</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;AbstractOperatorRestoreTestBase&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;SavepointMigrationTestBase&lt;/tt&gt; use &lt;tt&gt;SavepointSerializers#setFailWhenLegacyStateDetected&lt;/tt&gt; to disable the logic that fails reading savepoints when they contain legacy state.&lt;/p&gt;

